full_text:
On Juneteenth, we celebrate the end of slavery in America. Today in 1865, Union soldiers reached Galveston, TX with news that the Civil War was over.

It's a day to reflect, to celebrate how far we've come, and to reaffirm our resolve to create a better society for all Americans.

full_text:
My shoes haven’t looked this good in months, but they do now, thanks to Peoria’s own George Manias. For 74 years, George’s Shoeshine & Hatters has been a staple in Peoria, but #COVID19 closed his shop. It’s great to see him back in business.

Nobody does it better than George! https://t.co/UZY0WqXFue
